---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="uprooted">
  <div class="page">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="left">
        <h1>uprooted <span class="version">0.3.4</span></h1>
        <p class="sub">a client mod framework for root communications.</p>

        <ul class="features">
          <li>custom themes <span class="tag">working</span></li>
          <li>sentry blocker <span class="tag">working</span></li>
          <li>plugins <span class="tag">working</span></li>
          <li>bridge api <span class="tag tag-planned">planned</span></li>
          <li>settings injection <span class="tag">working</span></li>
        </ul>

        <a href="https://github.com/watchthelight/uprooted/releases/latest" class="download-btn">download</a>

        <nav>
          <a href="https://github.com/watchthelight/uprooted">source</a>
          <span class="dot">&middot;</span>
          <a href="https://rootapp.gg/AC0ILwUxgQqJ2MOSMXdGjw">server</a>
          <span class="dot">&middot;</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/watchthelight/uprooted/blob/main/LICENSE" class="dim">license</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="right">
        <div class="policy">
          <p>uprooted is a <strong>working beta</strong>. custom themes and the sentry blocker plugin ship with the framework. everything is configurable from Root's native settings panel.</p>
          <p>root's <a href="https://root.gg/terms">terms</a> prohibit reverse engineering and modification of the service. we believe cosmetic client mods can coexist with that policy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tos-box">
      <div class="tos-label">terms of use</div>
      <ol class="tos">
        <li><strong>do not distribute</strong> uprooted or its artifacts outside of the official repository.</li>
        <li><strong>do not discuss</strong> uprooted in Root's public channels, servers, or support.</li>
        <li>violations will result in your UUID being <strong>permanently blacklisted</strong>.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="tos-note">if you want to share uprooted, send them a link to the <a href="https://github.com/watchthelight/uprooted">repository</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="footer dim">not affiliated with root communications.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .columns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .left {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .right {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .version {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--green);
    border: 1px solid rgba(106, 154, 110, 0.3);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    margin-left: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .tag-planned {
    color: #c89040;
    border-color: rgba(200, 144, 64, 0.3);
  }

  .sub {
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features {
    list-style: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features li::before {
    content: "- ";
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  .download-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--green);
    color: #08080c;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    padding: 8px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .download-btn:hover {
    background: #7fb882;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  nav {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .dot {
    color: var(--dim);
    margin: 0 6px;
  }

  .dim {
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  .policy {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--dim);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--dim);
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  .policy strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .policy p + p {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .tos-box {
    margin-top: 32px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 80, 80, 0.25);
    background: rgba(200, 80, 80, 0.04);
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }

  .tos-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c85050;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .tos {
    list-style: none;
    counter-reset: tos;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .tos li {
    counter-increment: tos;
    padding: 2px 0;
  }

  .tos li::before {
    content: counter(tos) ". ";
    color: #c85050;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: none;
  }

  .tos li strong {
    color: #c85050;
  }

  .tos-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--dim);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .footer {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px;
    left: 32px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .columns {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      left: 20px;
    }
  }

  :global(html.dyslexia) .page {
    height: auto;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 64px;
    padding-bottom: 48px;
  }

  :global(html.dyslexia) .columns {
    gap: 40px;
  }

  :global(html.dyslexia) .footer {
    position: relative;
    bottom: auto;
    left: auto;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  :global(html.dyslexia) .policy {
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }

  :global(html.dyslexia) .tos {
    font-size: 11.5px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    :global(html.dyslexia) .page {
      padding-top: 72px;
    }
  }
</style>
